Package:        nqrustbackup-director-python-plugins-common
Architecture:   any
Section:        python
Pre-Depends:    debconf (>= 1.4.30) | debconf-2.0
Depends:        nqrustbackup-common (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - director Python plugin common files
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides common files for both Python director plugins.

Package:        nqrustbackup-contrib-director-python-plugins
Architecture:   any
Section:        python
Pre-Depends:    debconf (>= 1.4.30) | debconf-2.0
Depends:        nqrustbackup-common (= ${binary:Version}), nqrustbackup-director-python3-plugin (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Backup Archiving Recovery Open Sourced - contributed Director plugins
 NQRustBackup is a set of programs to manage backup, recovery and verification of
 data across a network of computers of different kinds.
 .
 This package provides additional NQRustBackup Director Python plugins, not part of the NQRustBackup project.
